"span> menija <span class=\"ui\">Dataja</span> składowanje wunuzować."

#: html/cool-help.html%2Bdiv.div.div.p:416-30
msgid ""
"Depending on the capabilities of your browser, the print window may appear "
"or a “Download PDF export?” popup appears. You can print this PDF in your "
"favorite PDF reader."
